Dr Adele is a very caring doctor that is very meticulous in her diagnosis of patients. She has lots of experience as well.

She gave me very good advice when my blood pressure reading taken in the clinic were high. Good and complete advice on how to monitor for a week at home, what type of blood pressure monitor to get, stop eating hawker food, eat home cooked food low in sodium at home how to meditate. In a few days time, my blood pressure were back to normal.
